OL,3,CThree teenagers charged with murder of
OL,4,CChloe Watson Dransfield
OL,6,FPolice have charged three teenagers
OL,7,Fwith the murder of a 16-year-old girl
OL,8,Fwho died in a stabbing in Leeds.
OL,10,FChloe Watson Dransfield was found
OL,11,Funconscious at an address on
OL,12,FKennerleigh Avenue in Austhorpe in the
OL,13,Fearly hours of Saturday morning.
OL,15,FShe was taken to hospital where she
OL,16,Fdied shortly later.
OL,18,FPolice have since confirmed she had
OL,19,Fbeen found with stab wounds and have
OL,20,Fcharged three young people with her
OL,21,Fmurder.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G1/3
