OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F369A1775063147
OL,3,CThree teenagers charged with murder of
OL,4,CChloe Watson Dransfield
OL,6,FKayla Smith, aged 18, of Kennerleigh
OL,7,FAvenue and Archie Rycroft, aged 19, of
OL,8,FMiddleton Park Road in Leeds are both
OL,9,Fcharged with murder and will appear at
OL,10,FLeeds Magistrates Court on Tuesday.
OL,11,FThey were remanded in custody.
OL,13,FA 17-year-old boy who cannot be named
OL,14,Fbecause of his age has also been
OL,15,Fcharged. West Yorkshire Police
OL,16,Fconfirmed all three self-defined as
OL,17,Fwhite British.
OL,19,FA further man, who is 18 and from
OL,20,FLeeds, has been arrested on suspicion
OL,21,Fof murder and remains in custody.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G2/3
