OL,3,CThree teenagers charged with murder of
OL,4,CChloe Watson Dransfield
OL,6,FAn 18-year-old woman and a 17-year-old
OL,7,Fboy who were arrested on suspicion of
OL,8,Fmurder have been released on bail
OL,9,Fpending further enquiries.
